room_title: Escape room "The Mystery of D.B. Cooper" by 59: Escape Adventures in Post Falls
room_address: 4294 W Riverbend Ave Post Falls, ID 83854
room_description:
Deep in the woods of the Pacific Northwest lies a mysterious cabin. You’ve heard rumors of it being D.B. Coopers hideout cabin. You and your friends are on a hiking expedition in this region and you’ve decided to see for yourself what the hype is all about.    

You wonder what will you discover? Money? Answers to long, lost questions? Evidence even the FBI could not locate? Maybe even D.B. Cooper himself? You could go down in history as THE person who cracked the case in the only un-solved skyjacking in U.S. history…  

Or will you wind up just being another story talked about by the locals and become part of the ongoing D.B. Cooper legend…
